228
00:13:02,000 --> 00:13:05,000
 They go to the bathroom and it becomes gross and contaminated.

229
00:13:05,000 --> 00:13:07,000
 But they drink from there. You want to know why?

230
00:13:07,000 --> 00:13:09,000
